reviewText: I have several other oin this series of cycling DVDs. They are great workouts and the photography is excellent. I feel as if I'm riding there myself! Would recommend and will continue to buy the other DVDs in this series that I don't already own.
This dvd is wonderful. The scenery is beautiful and motivating to keep riding.
I've got seven of these Virtual Active cycling DVD's, and they're all very good or better.  This one is no exception... outstanding value for the price.
